","tid":150263,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留左半年多啲<br />\n日日扎髻出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地一個月長幾多？<br />\n好想留快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你半年就紮到都叫長得好快<br />\n定你本身都唔短<br />\n我留咗一年鬆啲 而家先叫勉強紮到<br />\n不過我本身都幾短開始留</blockquote><br />\n我係前面同上面掘到髻, 後面同側面仲係好短(之前UNDERCUT)<br />\n我度過大概一個月先長1CM...."},{"pid":"3c166ead3c338081989ba860361bea84f561ee80","tid":150263,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"覺得趁仲有頭髮，點都要試下留長髮<br />\n但係好易出頭油，髮質又唔靚，唔知點留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e641382bec1c8d9a730c699a30e04c3186c20c","tid":150263,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留左半年多啲<br />\n日日扎髻出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地一個月長幾多？<br />\n好想留快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我留左年幾先扎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20aa38d597fade57f60cee8ba6a27dbff8aeaa66","tid":150263,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手上路<br />\n留左半年左右<br />\n但都係好鬼短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上天然卷 成日漲卜卜好似d唔知咩狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉天然卷係咪唔應該學人留長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n半年唔會長得去邊啦"},{"pid":"c2c3cedc50f815e032fefcb23d4141ae16285ba1","tid":150263,"uid":27303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"留左5個月 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf65c44329b9cb580178b07edbafa5d1949cae4","tid":150263,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQU54H8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQU54H8.jpg&h=e85854cb&s={SIZE}\" />依家唔長唔短中間位，側邊仲有排留，又未夠長紮<br />\n電左會唔會快長啲，又易啲打理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96d97e2a0958adddf5f3c403575a7cdbc098f13","tid":150263,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留左5個月 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾辛苦，唔長唔短過度期果陣，一夏天又熱到仆，次次都想剪黎短佢，但留到咁上下長，日後唔駛煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9071cfeee8e701f792d89d0a18236fce4b6e86e","tid":150263,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:12:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQU54H8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQU54H8.jpg&h=e85854cb&s={SIZE}\" />依家唔長唔短中間位，側邊仲有排留，又未夠長紮<br />\n電左會唔會快長啲，又易啲打理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留左幾耐？"},{"pid":"c0e7413fc5cb624db726c52972c34cf5c79ea948","tid":150263,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:12:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留左5個月 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾辛苦，唔長唔短過度期果陣，一夏天又熱到仆，次次都想剪黎短佢，但留到咁上下長，日後唔駛煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n忍"},{"pid":"73f4c491979c3936a89492258ef1438ea60589cb","tid":150263,"uid":27303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留左5個月 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾辛苦，唔長唔短過度期果陣，一夏天又熱到仆，次次都想剪黎短佢，但留到咁上下長，日後唔駛煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲要返緊office<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就快夏天喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa55219c5beed85c6fa477daf9ed77524d11d76","tid":150263,"uid":27303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQU54H8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQU54H8.jpg&h=e85854cb&s={SIZE}\" />依家唔長唔短中間位，側邊仲有排留，又未夠長紮<br />\n電左會唔會快長啲，又易啲打理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留左幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n我同你一樣都係紮到咁 後面又唔夠長連埋中間啲頭髮一齊紮 <br />\n側面就一pat野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c488f41d7fb942d2f17236eaea7564d9310988","tid":150263,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQU54H8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQU54H8.jpg&h=e85854cb&s={SIZE}\" />依家唔長唔短中間位，側邊仲有排留，又未夠長紮<br />\n電左會唔會快長啲，又易啲打理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留左幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n應該大半年到"},{"pid":"bc18170a3a8bd20ac2bcbffccae42416374ca989","tid":150263,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留左5個月 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾辛苦，唔長唔短過度期果陣，一夏天又熱到仆，次次都想剪黎短佢，但留到咁上下長，日後唔駛煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲要返緊office<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就快夏天喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返office唔怕喇"},{"pid":"24e28419dec52550b391bb049b0e039caa0928cd","tid":150263,"uid":3280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:40:03.000Z","msg":"有無俾人屌?<br />\n留過兩次都俾人屌到放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e95ce8448ac1379d8312dcf3663539f814b4906","tid":150263,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:41:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQU54H8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQU54H8.jpg&h=e85854cb&s={SIZE}\" />依家唔長唔短中間位，側邊仲有排留，又未夠長紮<br />\n電左會唔會快長啲，又易啲打理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留左幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n我同你一樣都係紮到咁 後面又唔夠長連埋中間啲頭髮一齊紮 <br />\n側面就一pat野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最主要係側邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似你講咁一pat野，又長得慢，<br />\n後面就唔怕，快長啲"},{"pid":"d364dcd92185ba0168d6eb8f90febab4fecea73d","tid":150263,"uid":28644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無俾人屌?<br />\n留過兩次都俾人屌到放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比人講兩句就放棄既話不如放棄埋人生啦"},{"pid":"095cdaa32900f9641b6ef33b8380f53ce17b151e","tid":150263,"uid":3280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無俾人屌?<br />\n留過兩次都俾人屌到放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比人講兩句就放棄既話不如放棄埋人生啦</blockquote><br />\n比上司屌呀"},{"pid":"58bd62bc65a7847a581ae4e53051ee8f7f7d3d8c","tid":150263,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:51:41.000Z","msg":"我留左7個月<br />\n因為之前鏟開兩邊後面<br />\n比較慢<br />\n頭頂就到下巴<br />\n後面而家成個唔剪頭髮毒撚咁<br />\n會抓住條頸"},{"pid":"a569af9eced43d65b1b2ea3294b3e0d83a9881a4","tid":150263,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無俾人屌?<br />\n留過兩次都俾人屌到放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比人講兩句就放棄既話不如放棄埋人生啦</blockquote><br />\n比上司屌呀</blockquote><br />\n咁唔係放棄<br />\n係冇得留"},{"pid":"86841b85e089988583ad41efb6d7135b30a7827f","tid":150263,"uid":27303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我留左7個月<br />\n因為之前鏟開兩邊後面<br />\n比較慢<br />\n頭頂就到下巴<br />\n後面而家成個唔剪頭髮毒撚咁<br />\n會抓住條頸</blockquote><br />\n認同最後個句<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fdb3e72fdb08f54bb73f36890a3eedeeec9327","tid":150263,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我留左7個月<br />\n因為之前鏟開兩邊後面<br />\n比較慢<br />\n頭頂就到下巴<br />\n後面而家成個唔剪頭髮毒撚咁<br />\n會抓住條頸</blockquote>產兩邊覺得無咁好睇，都係留晒紮先好睇"},{"pid":"673fbb8a6ebad1b9039f038170a4fdd077f02d98","tid":150263,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我留左7個月<br />\n因為之前鏟開兩邊後面<br />\n比較慢<br />\n頭頂就到下巴<br />\n後面而家成個唔剪頭髮毒撚咁<br />\n會抓住條頸</blockquote>產兩邊覺得無咁好睇，都係留晒紮先好睇</blockquote><br />\n我唔係留top knot<br />\n係留長頭髮之後有鏟兩邊<br />\n所以兩邊跟唔上頭頂"},{"pid":"2b4d2b81940d362ab74fc5223e824a98f6073945","tid":150263,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我留左7個月<br />\n因為之前鏟開兩邊後面<br />\n比較慢<br />\n頭頂就到下巴<br />\n後面而家成個唔剪頭髮毒撚咁<br />\n會抓住條頸</blockquote>產兩邊覺得無咁好睇，都係留晒紮先好睇</blockquote><br />\n我唔係留top knot<br />\n係留長頭髮<span style=\"color: red;\">之前</span>有鏟兩邊<br />\n所以兩邊跟唔上頭頂</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b7af58891c28c5c5b31abf0dd370b342217c4ac7","tid":150263,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:38:08.000Z","msg":"留左8個月好似<br />\n<br />\n想留日本果種長頭髮型唔想成日鏟則邊好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未留前我D頭髮去耳仔位，依家去到膊頭位左右<br />\n我覺得想快少少留長頭髮可以試下用椰子油滋潤個頭皮/髮根位同埋得閒修下髮尾（可以youtube 自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"a80230dc647786c5dcb1bbdad759c10d6603376c","tid":150263,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:42:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無俾人屌?<br />\n留過兩次都俾人屌到放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比人講兩句就放棄既話不如放棄埋人生啦</blockquote><br />\n比上司屌呀</blockquote><br />\nSor"},{"pid":"bb4e87e9d1b397d2d2adf315b55cf190e5feaeb4","tid":150263,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"點樣紮man bun紮得好睇？<br />\n自己成日紮得好亂 個型又唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5a5a82ad3fb723f4259a146c1ddb1c13e4bbbd","tid":150263,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留左8個月好似<br />\n<br />\n想留日本果種長頭髮型唔想成日鏟則邊好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未留前我D頭髮去耳仔位，依家去到膊頭位左右<br />\n我覺得想快少少留長頭髮可以試下用椰子油滋潤個頭皮/髮根位同埋得閒修下髮尾（可以youtube 自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</blockquote><br />\n巴打本身有用開定點？感覺如何"},{"pid":"e9073026b170bbfac57a223b9f9bfec532f10359","tid":150263,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣紮man bun紮得好睇？<br />\n自己成日紮得好亂 個型又唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪唔夠長只係勉強夠？<br />\n戴一陣頭cool先"},{"pid":"1deaa73ce18701d59d13186267990a35e4899748","tid":150263,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:29:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點樣紮man bun紮得好睇？<br />\n自己成日紮得好亂 個型又唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪唔夠長只係勉強夠？<br />\n戴一陣頭cool先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長到心口 夠就一定夠<br />\n不過點紮都唔多滿意<br />\n最後都係帶帽算"},{"pid":"6775000e5a23b50e83b4e5b078ab5cc73d86ccc5","tid":150263,"uid":8856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"咁多巴打話留長期間會戴帽遮柒<br />\n大家係戴邊類型既帽？"},{"pid":"864067ba93113a68c91d93f11178f4769c005ccf","tid":150263,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點樣紮man bun紮得好睇？<br />\n自己成日紮得好亂 個型又唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪唔夠長只係勉強夠？<br />\n戴一陣頭cool先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長到心口 夠就一定夠<br />\n不過點紮都唔多滿意<br />\n最後都係帶帽算</blockquote><br />\n巴打留左幾耐先到心口咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3ecd81b4dccb70752ede8ba029136e667624f8","tid":150263,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T15:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多巴打話留長期間會戴帽遮柒<br />\n大家係戴邊類型既帽？</blockquote><br />\nCap帽喳"},{"pid":"7925e3d5b9c9677412d942cd7e83bbc924a76398","tid":150263,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點樣紮man bun紮得好睇？<br />\n自己成日紮得好亂 個型又唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪唔夠長只係勉強夠？<br />\n戴一陣頭cool先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長到心口 夠就一定夠<br />\n不過點紮都唔多滿意<br />\n最後都係帶帽算</blockquote><br />\n巴打留左幾耐先到心口咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇返d相 好似1年8個月咁上下 <br />\n一去到膊頭就長得好快<br />\n唔知關唔關轉左洗頭水事"},{"pid":"143afcd7789410665ccee6f256cd6a41e5deb924","tid":150263,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多巴打話留長期間會戴帽遮柒<br />\n大家係戴邊類型既帽？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紳士帽 畫家帽 newsboy cap 冷帽 cap帽<br />\n其實都係睇你自己平時衣著係點"},{"pid":"2661801782b34fdbda8b51fb8f6ae99e94f15311","tid":150263,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點樣紮man bun紮得好睇？<br />\n自己成日紮得好亂 個型又唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪唔夠長只係勉強夠？<br />\n戴一陣頭cool先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長到心口 夠就一定夠<br />\n不過點紮都唔多滿意<br />\n最後都係帶帽算</blockquote><br />\n嗱利申定先 我自己唔係好夠長整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我幻想緊 會唔會跟啲女人咁紮住個頭瞓覺（可睇youtube 教學）<br />\n第二日起身個頭會「自然」曲<br />\n跟住先紮man bun 曲曲地有啲texture 應該會好睇啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXRXSGZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXRXSGZ.jpg&h=4f5c468e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n類似咁樣就好型"},{"pid":"f4996a0e8d2d9be070ac8d8c04842e1848547423","tid":150263,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"留名學野<br />\n<br />\n留咗半年, 唔長唔短, 則邊成日突起, 唔知點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df76f66ed5b17f98b6b2998ac4220e6b25048c1","tid":150263,"uid":7074,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/17/183826_1f97ebd1dc8d804a8597351af2afd13f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2F183826_1f97ebd1dc8d804a8597351af2afd13f.jpg&h=b725323e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留左年幾 諗緊剪定唔剪 因為想留埋左右 再加上依家扎黎扎去都唔滿意 帶帽又怪"},{"pid":"57740794003ea634c4718ef9d876a90f7e6d62cb","tid":150263,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/17/183826_1f97ebd1dc8d804a8597351af2afd13f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3