al/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe9e265beec9cbb5bb7eaf63931517b2c9c721b","tid":150263,"uid":79495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"想留, 但成日覺得如果無鬚會好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834fc4170722f778651180ff0faa796afd86d7a7","tid":150263,"uid":74299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:29:21.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n我係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留左n年.."},{"pid":"0b93e04193a95e77683ebe2c7da17284e33efb57","tid":150263,"uid":15558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"想留長髮無數次 有無人可以講下點樣支持同捱過中間唔長唔短日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0964d9a5a13891451b982cd6bee3cfc4b552e113","tid":150263,"uid":15826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"留過三次揮手 最長係而家 留咗一年幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4070664a7bfd95b4238cdf1afa704b5627aa44a","tid":150263,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留左兩年去到心口<br />\n跟住剪左<br />\n<br />\n剪完個個都話靚仔左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過都好視乎個人係幾時識<br />\n未留之前識嘅都話短髮靚仔<br />\n留之後識嘅話長髮文青feel/型啲<br />\n<br />\n不過我自己偏好長髮<br />\n而且剪完仲未習慣要朝朝gel頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想留嘅巴打唔好理人點睇<br />\n基本個個係唔長唔短個陣都會笑尻你<br />\n但你一有knot個下就會型棍好多"},{"pid":"0ba69e881cb16b9ad19929879f3c6ebac5f08c70","tid":150263,"uid":15826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想留長髮無數次 有無人可以講下點樣支持同捱過中間唔長唔短日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好冬天先開始留 因為夏天生得最快 冬天先留你柒嘅時間會拉長咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留到咁上下要修 如果唔係又會生得慢咗 電唔電睇個人 有啲人電咗好睇啲<br />\n夏天頂唔順可以學上面巴打咁兩邊undercut 但到你想留埋兩邊嗰時就會後悔 我後悔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3fe4adadfca25ce96328b30dba45f2be25d32d","tid":150263,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:59:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想留長髮無數次 有無人可以講下點樣支持同捱過中間唔長唔短日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好冬天先開始留 因為夏天生得最快 冬天先留你柒嘅時間會拉長咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留到咁上下要修 如果唔係又會生得慢咗 電唔電睇個人 有啲人電咗好睇啲<br />\n夏天頂唔順可以學上面巴打咁兩邊undercut 但到你想留埋兩邊嗰時就會後悔 我後悔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心undercut一長就好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你用頭"},{"pid":"5624492e53203c19bed0dc7a409bc812f4819481","tid":150263,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想留長髮無數次 有無人可以講下點樣支持同捱過中間唔長唔短日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好冬天先開始留 因為夏天生得最快 冬天先留你柒嘅時間會拉長咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留到咁上下要修 如果唔係又會生得慢咗 電唔電睇個人 有啲人電咗好睇啲<br />\n夏天頂唔順可以學上面巴打咁兩邊undercut 但到你想留埋兩邊嗰時就會後悔 我後悔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心undercut一長就好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你用頭</blockquote><br />\n*頭&quot;cool&quot;好過"},{"pid":"e46c00eb874fea8b783fb64004617c114b91c75b","tid":150263,"uid":31011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"暫時留到咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/230314_6319b5f962a6b7a1e16cee76bcc4937e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F230314_6319b5f962a6b7a1e16cee76bcc4937e.jpg&h=3a2b6054&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc97148a683ef0a446d9b41c4de9b4a5b4a08cfd","tid":150263,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:05:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暫時留到咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/19/230314_6319b5f962a6b7a1e16cee76bcc4937e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F19%2F230314_6319b5f962a6b7a1e16cee76bcc4937e.jpg&h=3a2b6054&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾好睇<br />\n電一電應該幾正"},{"pid":"f7181829e75c3ed464849221e3a18c39b501f91a","tid":150263,"uid":7074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c